::Battera::
She looked at Cybershark. She smiled. "Yeah, I"m alright. I think." 
she looked down and thought about how they had worked together. 
Cybershark, vulois and her. How they had worked for something. But 
she shook her head and looked at Cybershark. "Yeah, I'll be fine."  
She still stood there, her wings folded around her and waited for 
Vulois to answer her.  Then it struck her,"Why are you here 
Cybershark?"

stopped and transformed to bot mode and decloaked in the shadows.

ignoring Vulois.
